components.name: jaxb-core
components.description: JAXB Core module. Contains sources required by XJC, JXC and Runtime modules.

components.name: txw2
components.description: TXW is a library that allows you to write XML documents.

components.name: woodstox-core
components.description: Woodstox is a high-performance XML processor that implements Stax (JSR-173), SAX2 and Stax2 APIs

components.name: stax2-api
components.description: Stax2 API is an extension to basic Stax 1.0 API that adds significant new functionality, such as full-featured bi-direction validation interface and high-performance Typed Access API.

components.name: xmlschema-core
components.description: Commons XMLSchema is a light weight schema object model that can be used to manipulate or generate XML schema.

components.name: cxf-rt-security-saml
components.description: Apache CXF Runtime SAML Security functionality

components.name: xmlsec
components.description: Apache XML Security for Java supports XML-Signature Syntax and Processing, W3C Recommendation 12 February 2002, and XML Encryption Syntax and Processing, W3C Recommendation 10 December 2002. As of version 1.4, the library supports the standard Java API JSR-105: XML Digital Signature APIs.

components.name: commons-codec
components.description: The Apache Commons Codec component contains encoder and decoders for various formats such as Base16, Base32, Base64, digest, and Hexadecimal. In addition to these widely used encoders and decoders, the codec package also maintains a collection of phonetic encoding utilities.

components.name: metrics-core
components.description: Metrics is a Java library which gives you unparalleled insight into what your code does in production. Metrics provides a powerful toolkit of ways to measure the behavior of critical components in your production environment.

components.name: java-support
components.description: A POM containing properties, profiles, plugin configurations, etc. that are common across all Shibboleth V4 projects.

components.name: cryptacular
components.description: The spectacular complement to the Bouncy Castle crypto API for Java.

components.name: guava
components.description: Guava is a suite of core and expanded libraries that include utility classes, Google's collections, I/O classes, and much more.

components.name: failureaccess
components.description: Contains com.google.common.util.concurrent.internal.InternalFutureFailureAccess and InternalFutures. Most users will never need to use this artifact. Its classes is conceptually a part of Guava, but they're in this separate artifact so that Android libraries can use them without pulling in all of Guava (just as they can use ListenableFuture by depending on the listenablefuture artifact).

components.name: jasypt
components.description: Java library which enables encryption in java apps with minimum effort.
